{{!
Facebook meta tags to use when page has not facebook app to attach to.

Sadly these are not valid HTML5 as Facebook insist on using "property"
-attribute instead of the standard "name" attribute. Oh well..

Guide from: http://davidwalsh.name/facebook-meta-tags
You can debug these by using: https://developers.facebook.com/tools/debug

Different page types can be found from here: 
https://developers.facebook.com/docs/opengraphprotocol/#types

}}
{{#if site.meta.facebook}}
		{{verbose "facebook meta tags, for when user links this page to fb" 2}}
{{/if}}
{{#site.meta.facebook}}
{{! Site spesific }}
		<meta property="og:type" content="{{type}}"/>
		<meta property="og:site_name" content="{{site_name}}"/>
		<meta property="og:description" content="{{description}}">
{{! Page spesific }}
		<meta property="og:url" content="{{currentURL ..}}"/>
		<meta property="og:title" content="{{../title}}"/>
{{! Site/Page image }}
		<meta property="og:image" content="{{image}}"/>
		<link rel="image_src" href="{{image}}" />{{!
If the page has an like-button, then this should come handy:
		<meta property="fb:admins" content="USER_ID1,USER_ID2"/>
If there are multiple pages, and you want them all to point to one fb-page, link this:
		<meta property="fb:app_id" content="1234567"/>

Location is useful if your pages is a business profile or about anything else with a real-world location.
		<meta property="og:latitude" content="37.416343"/>
		<meta property="og:longitude" content="-122.153013"/>
		<meta property="og:street-address" content="1601 S California Ave"/>
		<meta property="og:locality" content="Palo Alto"/>
		<meta property="og:region" content="CA"/>
		<meta property="og:postal-code" content="94304"/>
		<meta property="og:country-name" content="USA"/>

If we want to have contact details visible for facebook:
}}
{{#contact}}
	{{#email}}
		<meta property="og:email" content="{{email}}"/>
	{{/email}}
	{{#phone}}
		<meta property="og:phone_number" content="{{phone}}"/>
	{{/phone}}
	{{#fax}}
		<meta property="og:fax_number" content="{{fax}}"/>
	{{/fax}}
{{/contact}}
{{/site.meta.facebook}}